-DOM is an acronym for "Document Object Model."
-DOM is created by the BROWSER.
-Once  HTML document is loaded , browser creates an object of the html document known as 'document' object.
-DOM hierarchy :
       html (root node)
         /\
        /  \       
       /    \  
     head    body
     /        / \
    /        /   \
 title      h1    div
                    /\
                   /  \
                   p   p